      "content": "it just feels like there's no light at the end of the tunnel anymore. like, i used to think if i just worked harder or stayed later, something would change. but now i realize i'm just chasing a ghost. everything i worked for is gone and i'm just... i'm so incredibly heavy. i feel like i'm just existing, not living. i just want the noise to stop. i just want to be able to rest without feeling guilty about it.",
